description: Gorgeous designer-renovated one-bedroom condo welcomes you home in stylish fashion.  Exposed beams and brick pay homage to historic Ft. Point building in the heart of Boston’s thriving Seaport district.  Eye-popping kitchen island is perfect for entertaining, topped with massive marble slab and loaded with Wolf wine fridge and beverage center.  Kitchen well-appointed with custom wrap-around cabinets, built-in Sub Zero refrigerator with freezer drawer, and beautiful 36” Wolf induction range with convection oven.  Stunning bathroom with marble shower, floating cabinets and heated floor.  New HVAC units.  Recently renovated lobby and common areas.  Phenomenal building foreman is extremely attentive.  Partial views of gorgeous Boston skyline.  Amazing restaurants and entertainment within two block radius. Financing options for down payment assistance available through seller.
